    public class DeleteElementPanel extends JPanel

    DialogFrame
    public class DialogFrame extends JDialog
    This is class that represents internal modal dialog on which you can place custom panel.
    And it is shown inside the instance of the main form and you can't do anything until you close the dialog.
    GeDocumentTabbedPane
    public class GeDocumentTabbedPane extends JTabbedPane implements Observer
    A custom JTabbedPane that visually represents GeDocuments in InternalFrame.
    It holds a model of project whose GeDocuments it represents,
    and a list of PageTabbedPane objects that it displays.
    PageTabbedPane
    public class PageTabbedPane extends JTabbedPane implements Observer
    A custom JTabbedPane instance that visually represents Pages as panels in the GeDocumentTabbedPane.
    RenameNodePanel
    public class RenameNodePanel extends JPanel
    This class represents panel which will be shown when user wants to rename the specific action.
    It contains 1 JTextField and 2 JButtons
    ShareDocumentPanel
    public class ShareDocumentPanel extends JPanel
    This class represents panel which will be shown when user wants to share GeDocument
    It contains an JList of all projects for user to choose from.
    TextEditorFrame
    This class represents a Text Editor in which the user inputs text and then displays it on the Slot, on close.
    TreeView
    public class TreeView extends JTree implements Observer
    This class represents JTree which is used for displaying the model.
